README

This is a Torch test problem of a simple uniform box.
It descends from:

    flash4.2.2-rad/source/Simulation/SimulationMain/
        DoubleSN
        SNSBBox

A tampered SN.F90 is provided for default SN/SNSBrandom unit.

    SN_SNSBrandom_SNejecta.F90

to be used with unit:

    SN/SNSBrandom/SNejecta/

Otherwise, doubleSN setup is done via flash.par config to SN/Simple.
